#~ "instance crashes the remaining will be unaffected. The disadvantage is "
#~ "that each &konqueror; instance uses more memory."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Der er ingen begrænsninger. Lige så mange instanser af &konqueror; som "
#~ "helst kan være åbne samtidigt. Fordelen ved dette er, at hvis en instans "
#~ "af &konqueror; bryder sammen, påvirkes de tilbageværende ikke. Bagdelen "
#~ "er at hver instans af &konqueror; bruger mere hukommelse."

#~ msgid "For file browsing only (recommended)"
#~ msgstr "Kun til filhåndtering (anbefales)"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "If this option is selected, you can have as many as you want &konqueror; "
#~ "instances open that are browsing the web, but only one instance of "
